License: 	GPLv2
Group: 		Networking/File transfer
Packager:	Motsyo Gennadi <drool@altlinux.ru>
Url:		http://fatrat.dolezel.info/
Source0:	http://www.dolezel.info/download/data/%name/%name-%version.tar.gz
